article_id:179,category_name:News,title_name:Summon Showcase Eastern Emissaries Now Available!,image_path:,message:<div>The Summon Showcase Eastern Emissaries starts <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1546236000"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>Event-specific adventurers, dragons, and wyrmprints will make their debuts in the summon showcase. Featured adventurers, dragons, and wyrmprints will also have increased appearance rates!</div><div><br></div><div>Limited-time adventurers, dragons, and wyrmprints:</div><div><br></div><div>■ Adventurers:</div><div>Ieyasu (shadow / blade), Sazanka (shadow / axe), and Addis (wind / blade)</div><div><br></div><div>■ Dragons:</div><div>Marishiten (shadow)</div><div><br></div><div>■ Wyrmprints:</div><div>Happy New Year!, Heralds of Hinomoto, Hanetsuki Rally</div><div><br></div><div>There&#39;s also a new wyrmprint that is not a limited-time wyrmprint called Vio Rhyse Alberia!</div><div><br></div><div>Note:For information about other featured adventurers, dragons, and wyrmprints, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured summons availability period:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1546236000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1547099940"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Some of the featured adventurers, dragons, and wyrmprints are detailed below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured Adventurer:</div><div><div class="summonPickUp">
